{
  "stem": "17135.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 252.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so the-- after three weeks, nobody knows what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out about it only at night that-- that they built the gallows there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was still working for the [? lagers. ?] And instead of-- they march everybody to the-- as usual, when the commanders came in, with the music, just like in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was regularly there to march to-- to-- to-- to-- to the music, although the could hardly walk, and they were counted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to match on the-- on the parade ground, and each block was counted, and [? blockalteste ?] reported how many people there to make sure that nobody is missing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then each of-- the minute the report was over, everyone was happy, can go to-- to the barrack to eat and to be able to sleep to forget about the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They forced them all to stand there, and three companies of us [? has ?] [? suddenly ?] arrived and circled the whole parade ground with heavy machine guns, and then suddenly the reflectors came up, and they board three Jewish boys, my brother and his two friends.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were all very haggard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Already-- apparently, didn't feed them anything there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They stepped on the platform that they prepared for them, and everyone was looking, and the SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then suddenly, all three of them started shouting that every could here it, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are the last one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are the last-- we are the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Courage, in other words, they didn't worry about their death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They worried about us, that we should not be demoralized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means [GERMAN], hold your head high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't despair.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- they the last ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody else will be hanged anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
